title: Nonito Donaire KOs Nordine Oubaali In Round 4 | SHOWTIME CHAMPIONSHIP BOXING
author: SHOWTIME Sports
description:
Surefire future Hall of Famer Nonito Donaire continued to make history and defy father time as he knocked out 118-lb champ Nordine Oubaali to become the oldest belt holder in division history. 

#SHOSports #NonitoDonaire #OubaaliDonaire
